dc_title_s: Atlantic City Expressway, New Jersey, outside cover
dc_description_s: Outside cover of Atlantic City Expressway route map (in Atlantic, Camden and Gloucester Counties, New Jersey). This side shows inset of interstate highways in the mid-Atlantic region, a directory of the expressways' toll plazas including toll dollar amount a guide to historic shrine, museums and points of interest, and a description of the expressways tolls, service charges, driving hints and emergency services.
